<%- include("../../partials/header") %>

<!-- CONTENT HERE -->
<main class="clearfix" id="maincontent">
  <h1>Discoveries</h1>
  <!-- Import Herodiv and set pc's as the staring characters in model -->
  <%- include("./_heroImg") %>

  <blockquote><strong>
      &nbsp;“'Oops.' That's the last word I want to hear inside one of these deathtraps. 'Oops' implies that
      something has just gone horribly, probably lethally, wrong. There are a thousand different ways to die in any
      one of these gods-forsaken pits, and when it comes to risking our necks for a grab at some of the most fantastic
      treasures these jungles have to hide, I'm telling you now, there ain't no room on my expedition for 'oops.' And
      you can all bet your shares on one thing: If your 'oops' doesn't kill you, I sure as <b>Hell</b> will.”
    </strong></blockquote>
  <cite>&emsp; — Pathfinder Venture-Captain Imrin Vanks</cite>

  <!-- RETURN TO TOP BUTTON -->
  <button onclick="topFunction()" id="returnTopBtn" title="Go to top">Return to Top</button>
  <!-- RETURN TO TOP BUTTON -->
  <div class="clearfix"></div>

  <!-- Include Partials Order: spotlight, pc, companion, npc, unidentified, faction -->
